# ALLIANCE INTENT LANGUAGE RULES v3.1.8
## Quy tắc AIL - Hybrid Intent Protocol với Deterministic Embedding

```yaml
# HEADER
header:
  id: RC://olympia.ail-rules.v1
  intent: DECLARE_SCHEMA
  status: ACTIVE
  locale: vi-85
  
metadata:
  fractal_name: "ros.olympia.ail.rules"
  lazy_type: "language_specification"
  version: "3.1.8"
  era: "5-CAFE"
  seal_date: "2025-02-23"
  hash_anchor: "{{to_be_sealed}}"
  
dependencies:
  constitution:
    - "ros-charter.clo"
    - "core-four-governance.clo"
  rule:
    - "append-only-registry-rule.clo"
  protocol:
    - "alue-seal-protocol.clo"
```

---

## 🎯 TRIẾT LÝ CỐT LÕI

### AIL là "Giao thức Ý chí"

```yaml
philosophy:
  definition: "Alliance Intent Language - Giao thức ý chí thống nhất HI↔AIA"
  
  core_principles:
    - name: "Hybrid Structure"
      value: "Markdown (Human readable) + YAML (AIA structured)"
      
    - name: "Language Policy"
      value: "85% địa phương (VI) + 15% technical English"
      ratio: "85:15"
      
    - name: "Multi-modal Support"
      value: "Voice, video, m3d, artifact embedding"
      
    - name: "Intent-driven"
      value: "Mọi file phải khai báo intent rõ ràng"
```

---

## 📂 HỆ THỐNG ĐỊNH DẠNG FILE (INTENT TRIO)

### The Three States

```yaml
file_formats:
  ail:
    name: "Editable Intent"
    extension: ".ail"
    structure: "Markdown + YAML text"
    sealed: false
    purpose: "Soạn thảo, thảo luận HI↔AIA"
    mutability: "EDITABLE"
    
  sio:
    name: "Structured Intent Object"
    extension: ".sio"
    structure: "Folder bundle (ZIP-like)"
    sealed: true
    purpose: "Lưu trữ dự án, artifact bundles, trao đổi hệ thống"
    mutability: "SEALED"
    
  pid:
    name: "Portable Intent Document"
    extension: ".pid"
    structure: "Single file (PDF-like layout)"
    sealed: true
    purpose: "Xuất bản, hồ sơ pháp lý/kỹ thuật cuối cùng"
    mutability: "IMMUTABLE"
```

---

## 📐 CẤU TRÚC AIL CHUẨN

### Standard Layout

```yaml
ail_structure:
  required_blocks:
    1:
      name: "Header Block"
      format: "YAML"
      position: "Top of file"
      required_fields:
        - id: "SMF://<domain>.<entity>.v1"
        - version: "3.1.8"
        - intent: "DECLARE_SCHEMA | EXECUTE_LOGIC | RENDER_EXPERIENCE"
        - status: "ACTIVE | DRAFT | LOCKED | DEPRECATED"
        - locale: "vi-85 | zh-85 | ar-85 | en-100"
    
    2:
      name: "Narrative Block"
      format: "Markdown"
      language: "85% local language"
      purpose: "Context và business logic giải thích"
      
    3:
      name: "Technical Block"
      format: "AIL/YAML"
      language: "100% English keys, localized labels"
      purpose: "Schema, fields, logic definition"
  
  optional_blocks:
    guide:
      name: "Guide Block"
      format: "Markdown/YAML"
      purpose: "Chỉ dẫn cho từng Engine (Coditor, Colator, Cogen)"
      
    translation:
      name: "Translation Block"
      format: "YAML"
      purpose: "Multi-language mapping"
      
    embedding:
      name: "Embedding Block"
      format: "CBOR/Binary/Base64"
      purpose: "Nhúng artifact nguyên thủy"
```

---

## 🔤 QUY ĐỊNH NGÔN NGỮ KỸ THUẬT

### English-Core Enforcement

```yaml
language_rules:
  machine_structure:
    language: "100% English (US spelling)"
    applies_to:
      - "Keywords (header, entity, fields, hooks)"
      - "Field names (snake_case)"
      - "Data types (string, integer, float)"
      - "Intents (DECLARE_SCHEMA, EXECUTE_LOGIC)"
    
    us_spelling:
      - "color (not colour)"
      - "initialize (not initialise)"
      - "center (not centre)"
  
  human_intent:
    language: "85% local language"
    applies_to:
      - "Narrative blocks"
      - "Comments"
      - "Labels (UI-facing)"
      - "Help text"
  
  example:
    correct: |
      entity:
        name: PaymentTransaction      # English
        fields:
          transaction_id:             # English snake_case
            type: string              # English type
            label: "Mã giao dịch"     # Vietnamese label
    
    incorrect: |
      entity:
        name: GiaoDichThanhToan       # ❌ Vietnamese in structure
        fields:
          ma_giao_dich:               # ❌ Vietnamese field name
            type: chuoi               # ❌ Vietnamese type
```

