## 🔗 DETERMINISTIC EMBEDDING RULES (NEW REFINEMENT)

### CRD Audit Refinements

```yaml
origin_integrity:
  required: true
  fields:
    source_type:
      enum: ["local", "poly-ledger", "remote"]
    source_hash: "SHA256"
    canonicalization:
      enum: ["rfc_8785", "rfc_8949_deterministic", "rust_norm_v1"]
  
  validation:
    rule: "Loader MUST verify origin before trust"
    action_on_missing: "REJECT"

embedding_constraints:
  authority_boundary:
    allow_in_domains:
      - "spec"
      - "blueprint"
      - "engine"
      - "protocol"
      - "rule"
    forbid_in_domains:
      - "constitution"
    
    constitution_rule:
      inline_embedding: false
      hash_reference: true
      reason: "Constitution không được chứa executable binary"

rust_norm_v1:
  specification:
    newline: "LF"
    trim_trailing_space: true
    ensure_trailing_newline: true
    remove_doc_hidden: false
    tab_policy: "preserve"
  
  reproducibility:
    guarantee: "Same source → same hash"
    test: "rustfmt --check + sha256sum"

hash_standard:
  primary: "SHA256"
  bundle_merkle: "SHA256"
  future_upgrade:
    authority: "seal-integrity-law.clo only"
    forbidden: "Arbitrary hash function change"

ordering_scope:
  yaml_keys: "ascii_lexicographic"
  manifest_entries: "stable_sorted"
  merkle_leaves: "index_sorted"
  locale: "C (POSIX) - không locale-dependent"
```

### Embedding Primitives

```yaml
embedding_protocol:
  purpose: "Nhúng artifact nguyên thủy vào .ail/.sio với deterministic guarantee"
  
  primitive_classes:
    canonical_data:
      - "json_rfc_8785"
      - "cbor_rfc_8949_deterministic"
    source_code:
      - "rust_normalized"
    binary_blob:
      - "image_prehashed"
  
  supported_formats:
    cbor:
      mime_type: "application/cbor"
      encoding: "raw binary OR base64"
      deterministic: true
      use_case: "Structured data với canonical serialization"
      canonicalization: "rfc_8949_deterministic"
      
    rust:
      mime_type: "text/x-rust"
      encoding: "utf-8 text"
      deterministic: true
      use_case: "Macro code, RFN implementation"
      hash_strategy: "Normalize whitespace before hash"
      
    json:
      mime_type: "application/json"
      encoding: "utf-8 text"
      deterministic: "Requires canonical JSON"
      use_case: "Configuration, API schema"
      canonicalization: "RFC 8785 (JCS)"
      
    image:
      mime_type: "image/jpeg | image/png"
      encoding: "base64"
      deterministic: true
      use_case: "Diagrams, screenshots, proofs"
      hash_strategy: "Hash before base64 encode"
```

---

## 📦 EMBEDDING METHODS

### Three Embedding Strategies

```yaml
embedding_methods:
  inline:
    name: "Inline Embedding"
    when: "Small artifacts (< 100KB)"
    format: "base64 trong YAML block"
    deterministic: "YES - content hashed directly"
    
    example: |
      artifact:
        type: "image/jpeg"
        encoding: "base64"
        hash: "SHA256:abc123..."
        data: "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAA..."
  
  reference:
    name: "Hash Reference"
    when: "Large artifacts (> 100KB)"
    format: "Hash pointer + external storage"
    deterministic: "YES - hash anchored"
    
    example: |
      artifact:
        type: "application/cbor"
        hash: "SHA256:def456..."
        location: "poly-ledger://artifact/def456"
        size: 2048576
  
  bundle:
    name: "Bundle Embedding (.sio)"
    when: "Multiple related artifacts"
    format: "Folder structure in ZIP-like container"
    deterministic: "YES - manifest với ordered list"
    
    example: |
      manifest.ail:
        artifacts:
          - name: "schema.cbor"
            hash: "SHA256:abc..."
          - name: "macro.rs"
            hash: "SHA256:def..."
          - name: "diagram.jpg"
            hash: "SHA256:ghi..."
```

---

## 🔐 DETERMINISTIC GUARANTEE RULES

### Ensuring Determinism

```yaml
deterministic_rules:
  canonical_ordering:
    rule: "Tất cả list phải có thứ tự xác định"
    method: "Lexicographic sort by key/filename"
    example:
      before: "[c.rs, a.rs, b.rs]"
      after: "[a.rs, b.rs, c.rs]"
  
  whitespace_normalization:
    rule: "Text artifacts phải normalize whitespace"
    applies_to: ["*.rs", "*.ail", "*.json"]
    method: "Trim trailing, normalize newlines to LF"
    
  json_canonicalization:
    rule: "JSON phải canonical trước khi hash"
    standard: "RFC 8785 (JSON Canonicalization Scheme)"
    library: "canonicaljson-rs"
    
  cbor_deterministic:
    rule: "CBOR phải dùng deterministic encoding"
    standard: "RFC 8949 Section 4.2"
    library: "ciborium with canonical flag"
    
  image_hash:
    rule: "Image hash trước khi encode base64"
    flow: "binary → SHA256 → store hash → base64 encode"
    reason: "Base64 có thể có padding variants"
```

---

## 📋 EMBEDDING BLOCK SYNTAX

### Standard Embedding Block

```yaml
embedding_syntax:
  inline_example: |
    ```ail
    embeddings:
      diagram:
        id: "authority-boundary-diagram"
        type: "image/png"
        encoding: "base64"
        hash: "SHA256:abc123def456..."
        origin:
          source_type: "local"
          source_hash: "SHA256:abc123def456..."
          canonicalization: "prehashed"
        timestamp: "2025-02-23T08:00:00Z"
        data: |
          iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAUA
          AAAFCAYAAACNbyblAAAAHElEQVQI
          12P4//8/w38GIAXDIBKE0DHxgljN
          BAAqqQGAAAD//8yvnQAAAABJRU5E
          rkJggg==
    ```
  
  reference_example: |
    ```ail
    embeddings:
      macro_code:
        id: "override-precedence-macro"
        type: "text/x-rust"
        hash: "SHA256:def456ghi789..."
        origin:
          source_type: "poly-ledger"
          source_hash: "SHA256:def456ghi789..."
          canonicalization: "rust_norm_v1"
        location: "poly-ledger://code/def456ghi789"
        size: 4096
        metadata:
          compiled_at: "2025-02-23T08:30:00Z"
          compiler_version: "rustc 1.75.0"
    ```
  
  bundle_example: |
    ```ail
    bundle:
      manifest_version: "1.0"
      artifacts:
        - id: "schema"
          filename: "payment-schema.cbor"
          hash: "SHA256:abc..."
          
        - id: "implementation"
          filename: "payment-logic.rs"
          hash: "SHA256:def..."
          
        - id: "test_data"
          filename: "fixtures.json"
          hash: "SHA256:ghi..."
      
      integrity_proof:
        method: "Merkle Tree"
        root_hash: "SHA256:xyz..."
    ```
```

---

## 🧬 EMBEDDING IN .sio BUNDLES

### .sio Structure

```yaml
sio_structure:
  format: "ZIP-like container"
  
  required_files:
    manifest:
      filename: "manifest.ail"
      purpose: "List of all artifacts với hash"
      
    seal:
      filename: "seal.log"
      purpose: "Signature và timestamp"
  
  artifact_layout:
    example: |
      payment-module.sio/
      ├── manifest.ail
      ├── seal.log
      ├── artifacts/
      │   ├── schema.cbor
      │   ├── logic.rs
      │   ├── test.json
      │   └── diagram.jpg
      └── metadata/
          └── build.yaml
  
  deterministic_packing:
    rule: "Files phải packed theo thứ tự lexicographic"
    compression: "Store only (no compression) OR deterministic gzip"
    timestamp: "Normalized to UTC, zero out filesystem metadata"
```

---

## 🔍 HASH VERIFICATION FLOW

### Verification Process

```yaml
verification_flow:
  step_1:
    name: "Extract artifact"
    action: "Read từ .ail embedding OR .sio bundle"
    
  step_2:
    name: "Decode if needed"
    action: "base64 decode nếu inline embedded"
    
  step_3:
    name: "Canonicalize"
    action: "Apply normalization rules (whitespace, JSON, CBOR)"
    
  step_4:
    name: "Compute hash"
    method: "SHA256"
    
  step_5:
    name: "Compare"
    test: "computed_hash == declared_hash"
    action_on_match: "TRUST"
    action_on_mismatch: "REJECT + ALERT"
```

---

## 🚫 FORBIDDEN EMBEDDING PRACTICES

### Anti-patterns

```yaml
forbidden:
  non_deterministic_compression:
    example: "gzip with default settings (timestamps embedded)"
    reason: "Khác nhau mỗi lần compress"
    
  unsorted_lists:
    example: "artifacts: [c.rs, a.rs, b.rs]"
    reason: "Thứ tự không xác định → hash khác"
    
  raw_json_without_canonicalization:
    example: '{"b": 2, "a": 1}'
    reason: "Key order không đảm bảo → hash khác"
    
  filesystem_metadata:
    example: "ZIP with creation timestamps"
    reason: "Metadata thay đổi → hash khác"
    
  relative_paths:
    example: "../../../secret.rs"
    reason: "Path traversal security risk"
```

---

## ✅ BEST PRACTICES

### Recommended Patterns

```yaml
best_practices:
  small_artifacts:
    size: "< 100KB"
    method: "Inline embedding với base64"
    benefit: "Self-contained, easy verification"
    
  large_artifacts:
    size: "> 100KB"
    method: "Hash reference + poly-ledger storage"
    benefit: "Giảm kích thước .ail, fast lookup"
    
  multiple_artifacts:
    count: "> 3 related files"
    method: "Bundle in .sio"
    benefit: "Atomic versioning, single seal"
    
  code_artifacts:
    type: "*.rs, *.ts, *.py"
    preprocessing:
      - "Strip comments (optional, document decision)"
      - "Normalize whitespace"
      - "Format with deterministic formatter"
    
  binary_artifacts:
    type: "*.cbor, *.jpg, *.wasm"
    preprocessing: "None - hash directly"
    encoding: "base64 for inline, raw for bundle"
```

