## 📐 INTEGRATION WITH CLO SYSTEM

### CLO ↔ AIL Relationship

```yaml
clo_ail_integration:
  clo_files:
    format: ".clo (Canon List Object)"
    structure: "AIL-compliant"
    purpose: "Hace rule definitions"
    
  ail_in_clo:
    rule: "CLO files MUST use AIL v3.1.8 format"
    header: "Required với RC:// or SMF:// prefix"
    
  embedding_in_clo:
    allowed: true
    use_case: "Embed Rust macro, CBOR schema, test fixtures"
    example: |
      # File: override-precedence-law.clo
      embeddings:
        macro:
          filename: "precedence_resolver.rs"
          hash: "SHA256:abc..."
          data: "{{inline or reference}}"
  
  sio_for_clo_bundles:
    use_case: "Package related CLO + artifacts"
    example: "constitution-bundle.sio containing all P0 CLO"
```

