## 🔐 SEAL & INTEGRITY

### AIL Sealing Protocol

```yaml
sealing:
  ail_files:
    status: "UNSEALED by default"
    transition: ".ail → .sio or .pid for sealing"
    
  sio_files:
    status: "SEALED"
    method: "Digital signature + timestamp"
    immutability: "Cannot unpack and repack without breaking seal"
    
  pid_files:
    status: "IMMUTABLE"
    method: "Cryptographic seal + layout lock"
    use_case: "Legal documents, final deliverables"
  
  hash_anchoring:
    embedded_artifacts: "Each artifact has individual hash"
    container: ".sio has Merkle tree root hash"
    verification: "Verify individual → verify tree → verify seal"
```

