## 📊 DETERMINISTIC BUILD GUARANTEE

### Build Reproducibility

```yaml
deterministic_build:
  goal: "Cùng input → cùng output hash"
  
  requirements:
    - "Canonical ordering of all lists"
    - "Normalized whitespace in text"
    - "Canonical JSON/CBOR serialization"
    - "No embedded timestamps (except in seal.log)"
    - "No filesystem metadata in archives"
  
  verification:
    test: "Build 2 lần ở 2 máy khác nhau"
    expect: "SHA256 của .sio identical"
    
  ci_cd_integration:
    tool: "Reproducible build checker"
    frequency: "Every commit"
    action_on_fail: "Block merge"
```

