## 🧪 TESTING EMBEDDINGS

### Verification Test Suite

```yaml
testing:
  hash_verification:
    test: "Load embedded artifact, compute hash, compare"
    expect: "Match"
    
  canonical_json:
    test: '{"b":2,"a":1} → canonicalize → {"a":1,"b":2}'
    expect: "Same hash every time"
    
  cbor_determinism:
    test: "Encode same data 100 times"
    expect: "Identical bytes"
    
  sio_rebuild:
    test: "Unpack → repack .sio"
    expect: "Same hash (if deterministic packing)"
    
  cross_platform:
    test: "Build .sio on Linux, Mac, Windows"
    expect: "Identical hashes"
```

