## 🔗 APPENDIX: EMBEDDING EXAMPLES

### Example 1: Inline Rust Macro

```ail
embeddings:
  precedence_macro:
    id: "override-precedence-resolver"
    type: "text/x-rust"
    encoding: "utf-8"
    hash: "SHA256:1a2b3c4d5e6f..."
    normalized: true
    data: |
      #[macro_export]
      macro_rules! resolve_precedence {
          ($domain:expr, $weights:expr) => {
              $weights.get($domain).unwrap_or(&0.0)
          };
      }
```

### Example 2: Referenced CBOR Schema

```ail
embeddings:
  payment_schema:
    id: "payment-transaction-schema"
    type: "application/cbor"
    hash: "SHA256:9z8y7x6w5v..."
    location: "poly-ledger://schema/9z8y7x6w5v"
    size: 2048
    metadata:
      version: "1.0"
      created: "2025-02-23"
```

### Example 3: .sio Bundle Manifest

```ail
bundle:
  name: "constitution-p0-bundle"
  version: "1.0"
  sealed: true
  
  artifacts:
    - filename: "override-precedence-law.clo"
      hash: "SHA256:aaa111..."
      
    - filename: "authority-boundary-law.clo"
      hash: "SHA256:bbb222..."
      
    - filename: "seal-integrity-law.clo"
      hash: "SHA256:ccc333..."
  
  merkle_root: "SHA256:xyz789..."
  signature: "ED25519:signature_here..."
```
